Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.19,0:01:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ironheart guided me to the Gate of Mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which lies deep within the Stone Wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a place where wandering souls gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it's a place where you can confront your own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once there, I met the soul of my Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Through a Duel, he was able to relay his feelings to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm no longer in doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Orichalcos Soldier"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner, you always...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use your card to slit my throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}HERE I GO, KAIBA!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you, Other... Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my sake...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who had the {\i1}true{\i0} courage...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't {\i1}me{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The True Duelist here, Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}you{\i0}...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've gone there, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, the nameless Pharaoh's soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up, Rafael.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That place is home to the Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot possibly step foot in there in your current state.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the shard of Orichalcos...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and toss it down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you've noticed us...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is {\i1}this{\i0} thing...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's resurrected the servant of evil forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Servant of evil forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Lord Dartz's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dispose of the Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's about to happen...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That vision just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's Kris!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ironheart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this beast...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That creature dates back to the ancient days of my time period.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spirits of the soldiers who served under Altantis's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers of Atlantis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can say with confidence that this is the sacred ground we ruled over along with the Atlantis soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trapped...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It Summoned a Monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Gigas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send the nameless Pharaoh to his doom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The souls of our comrades sleeping within this terrain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Duel Disk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spirits shall aid your Monsters with the power they require!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Monsters...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me out, my Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself!\N Winged Phantom Beast Chimera!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimera Impact Dash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!? This beast regenerated with a power-up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimera!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this Monster gains Attack Points whenever it's destroyed...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the Magic Card Fissure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Cards have no effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Barrier - Mirror Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traps won't work either...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retrained Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes on... I'm done for...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless... Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be bad if we let it continue...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Timaeus...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This shall be our final mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}O Legendary Dragon, Timaeus...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let us return peace and harmony to this land once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's the meaning of this vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ironheart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kris! Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beseech thee, Thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crash down asunder, ablaze the form of a speeding rabbit! Tear through my enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great "Legendary Dragon"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The evil spirits are being drawn towards my grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunny!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kris!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thy spirits lying in the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grant me thine divine protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel Monsters...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who {\i1}is{\i0} he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kris...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironheart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who exactly are you guys...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironheart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You annoying ghost from the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out my my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I beseech thee, Thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironheart!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nameless Pharaoh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Timaeus card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironheart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironheart!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kris...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Take this card...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...our task...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kris!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuriboh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kris!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this, Kris! Stay away from me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kris!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kris!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are... our last hope...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... save... the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kris...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kris!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Timaeus...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't just my fight...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kris...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ironheart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What you can see, yet cannot see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's something very important to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I no longer have any doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's meant to protect that very same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grant me your power once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timaeus...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh! Have you brought back the Legendary Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Combine with Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Knight Black Magician Girl!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, a Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack, Dragon Knight Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Dragon Burst!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hermos card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has something happened to Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timaeus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please fight alongside me once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're back to normal, Nameless Pharaoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall be the one to defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these guys were warriors who fought alongside the Legendary Dragon ages ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their souls were trying to guide you, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget what you guys have done for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your will, I will definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:22:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.54,0:22:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironheart and Chris...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harboring their memories, Yugi has gained new motivation to take down Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's spirit has grown considerably while facing this large ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, as for Otogi-{\i1}kun{\i0} and the others we left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They encounter one of Doma's Musketeers, Varon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be reckless! Rebecca! Otogi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Varon Engages!\N The Mysterious Armor Deck"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
